#!/usr/bin/env bash
# comfyui-decay-risk-medium-last-u.sh — ComfyUI 节点工作流搭建与复用（工程链）(Decay risk: medium) last_updated: 2026-06-22 SOP walkthrough for AIGC 创作工作流.
